<div class="container content">
    <p>At <strong>Book Cloud</strong>, we are committed to safeguarding the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you interact with our platform.</p>

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you register on our platform, we collect your name, email address, and login credentials.</li>
        <li><strong>Reading Activity:</strong> We store data related to your reading preferences and download history to enhance your user experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Device and Usage Data:</strong> We collect non-personal data like browser type, IP address, and session duration to improve site performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To create and manage your user account</li>
        <li>To provide personalized book recommendations</li>
        <li>To improve our services and user interface</li>
        <li>To send essential account-related communications</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. Password Security</h4>
    <p>We use <strong>BCrypt encryption</strong> to securely store your passwords in our database. This ensures that your credentials remain safe and inaccessible to unauthorized parties.</p>

    <h4>4. Sharing of Information</h4>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. Your data is only used internally for platform improvements and user support.</p>

    <h4>5. Cookies</h4>
    <p>Book Cloud uses cookies to remember user preferences and sessions. You may disable cookies via your browser settings, but this may limit certain features.</p>

    <h4>6. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You may contact us at <a href="mailto:support@bookcloud.com">support@bookcloud.com</a> for data-related requests.</p>

    <h4>7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised "Last Updated" date.</p>

